  "description": "<h4>Features</h4>\n<ul>\n  <li>Universal fit for a wide range of turbo applications, slip fit inlets and outlets</li>\n  <li>The new intercooler maximizes space in the already narrow bumper area, increasing size and volume; reduces temperatures up to 40°F and adds nearly 20 horsepower on modified cars compared to the stock core</li>\n  <li>Constructed from cast aluminum with a bar and plate design, increasing both cross-sectional and frontal surface area by 50%+, dramatically improving performance on and off the track</li>\n  <li>High-flow cast end tanks are TIG welded; all joints TIG welded to prevent cracking and wear; excellent quality and durability</li>\n  <li>Made of high-quality durable T-6061 aluminum, can withstand up to 500°F; each end tank features precision CNC machined hose fittings compatible with factory intercooler hoses</li>\n  <li>The accessories in the photos are included</li>\n  <li>1 year warranty for any manufacturing defect</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h4>Technical Specifications</h4>\n<ul>\n  <li>\n<strong>Cooling Type:</strong> Air to Air</li>\n  <li>\n<strong>Core Construction:</strong> Bar and Plate</li>\n  <li>\n<strong>Overall Size:</strong> 27 x 6 x 2.5 in.</li>\n  <li>\n<strong>Core Size:</strong> 22 x 6 x 2.5 in.</li>\n  <li>\n<strong>Inlet Size:</strong> 2.25 in.</li>\n  <li>\n<strong>Outlet Size:</strong> 2.25 in.</li>\n  <li>\n<strong>Flow Rate:</strong> 330 CFM @ 28 inH2O (1 psi), 540 CFM @ 50 inH2O (2 psi)</li>\n  <li>\n<strong>HP Rating:</strong> 800 HP</li>\n  <li>\n<strong>Material:</strong> T-6061 aluminum</li>\n  <li>\n<strong>Finish:</strong> Polished</li>\n</ul>\n",
